|---|---|
| **MISTRAL_V7** | Contains `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` |
| **MISTRAL_V1** | Contains `[INST]` + ` [INST]` (space before) + `' [INST] ' + system_message` |
| **MISTRAL_V3_TEKKEN** | Contains `[INST]` + `"[INST]"` (quoted) + `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` |
| **MISTRAL_V3** | Contains `[INST]` + `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` (but not above patterns) |

