- `[INST]...[/INST]` for user messages
- `[THINK]...[/THINK]` for reasoning content
- `[TOOL_CALLS]` introduces tool calls
- `[ARGS]` contains function arguments
- `[TOOL_RESULTS]...[/TOOL_RESULTS]` for tool results

